1
00:00:17,559 --> 00:00:19,477
YOUN HYUN-JAE

2
00:00:19,561 --> 00:00:21,479
SONG SEUNG-IL

3
00:00:21,563 --> 00:00:23,481
PARK HEE-SUN

4
00:00:23,565 --> 00:00:25,483
SHIN HYEON-WOO

5
00:00:25,567 --> 00:00:27,485
KIM GO-EUN

6
00:00:27,569 --> 00:00:29,404
KIM JAE-JIN

7
00:00:29,487 --> 00:00:31,489
HAM YE-JIN

8
00:00:31,573 --> 00:00:33,491
WOO SUNG-MIN

9
00:00:33,575 --> 00:00:35,493
KIM MIN-GEE

10
00:00:35,577 --> 00:00:37,495
LIM SU-BEEN

11
00:00:37,579 --> 00:00:39,497
LEE SUNG-HUN

12
00:00:39,581 --> 00:00:41,499
LEE JOO-YOUNG

13
00:00:41,583 --> 00:00:43,501
CHOI MINA SUE

14
00:00:43,585 --> 00:00:45,503
LEE HA-EUN

15
00:00:45,587 --> 00:00:47,505
JO I-GEON

16
00:00:52,469 --> 00:00:54,929
SINGLE'S INFERNO

17
00:00:59,976 --> 00:01:03,271
I feel like I'm gonna throw up.
I might be sick.

18
00:01:03,354 --> 00:01:04,814
- Motion sickness?
- I feel it.

19
00:01:14,574 --> 00:01:15,700
- Mina Sue.
- Will she notice?

20
00:01:15,784 --> 00:01:16,618
For sure.

21
00:01:21,581 --> 00:01:23,792
She's seen it!

22
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:25,543
She's seen it!

23
00:01:25,627 --> 00:01:28,004
- Oh, she saw it for sure.
- Definitely.

24
00:02:00,286 --> 00:02:02,539
It's not like Mina Sue
can lean on Seung-il's shoulder,

25
00:02:02,622 --> 00:02:04,165
given their situation, can she?

26
00:02:04,249 --> 00:02:07,252
Because last night, she was like,
"Don't tell me what to do."

27
00:02:07,335 --> 00:02:09,087
That's enough to make her give up on him.

28
00:02:09,170 --> 00:02:12,423
The reason I have a bad feeling about this
is because it would be okay

29
00:02:12,507 --> 00:02:14,134
if this were the last episode, you know?

30
00:02:14,217 --> 00:02:16,469
But we still have
quite a few episodes to go.

31
00:02:16,553 --> 00:02:18,346
That's right. We're on day seven.

32
00:02:18,429 --> 00:02:21,558
- Three nights and four days left.
- That's a lot of time.

33
00:02:21,641 --> 00:02:24,686
That's enough time to build the
Great Wall of China several times over.

34
00:02:26,104 --> 00:02:27,605
Oh, this looks good.

35
00:02:27,689 --> 00:02:30,233
- Enjoy your meal.
- Dig in, everybody.

36
00:02:36,322 --> 00:02:37,782
The weather is awesome today.

37
00:02:40,285 --> 00:02:41,286
It is nice weather.

38
00:02:44,747 --> 00:02:46,374
Min-gee looks so sad.

39
00:02:46,457 --> 00:02:50,211
Don't worry, because Seung-il's
going to come back a changed man.

40
00:02:50,295 --> 00:02:52,172
He'll be back with his mind made up.

41
00:02:54,257 --> 00:02:56,426
Why are we back here?

42
00:02:57,969 --> 00:02:59,762
- Get the chopper.
- We're here.

43
00:03:06,227 --> 00:03:08,479
- They're coming, they're here.
- Are they?

44
00:03:08,563 --> 00:03:11,065
- They are.
- They're back already?

45
00:03:11,149 --> 00:03:12,901
Yeah, they are. They're all back.

46
00:03:12,984 --> 00:03:13,818
They are?

47
00:03:13,902 --> 00:03:15,320
Oh, they are.

48
00:03:16,821 --> 00:03:19,073
Looks like they had a good time.

49
00:03:22,952 --> 00:03:25,330
- Let's get up.
- Yeah. Let's get up. Let's go.

50
00:03:29,334 --> 00:03:31,628
- Mm.
- Did you have a good time there?

51
00:03:31,711 --> 00:03:34,255
- Hello.
- Hello.

52
00:03:34,339 --> 00:03:35,423
Did you have a good time?

53
00:03:38,218 --> 00:03:39,594
- Go-eun, join me.
- Huh?

54
00:03:44,474 --> 00:03:45,391
Hey.

55
00:03:47,018 --> 00:03:49,812
Hang on a second.
I didn't even get to say hello to them.

56
00:03:49,896 --> 00:03:51,689
- Huh?
- What?

57
00:03:53,483 --> 00:03:55,235
- Was the trip okay?
- Yeah.

58
00:03:55,318 --> 00:03:57,153
- Did you have fun?
- Yeah.

59
00:03:58,029 --> 00:04:00,156
You want to do this now?

60
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,824
- Couldn't it wait?
- It couldn't.

61
00:04:01,908 --> 00:04:04,244
Of course, it couldn't wait any longer.

62
00:04:06,329 --> 00:04:09,582
- We've been waiting for you.
- Hello. You're back.

63
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:10,792
Hello.

64
00:04:12,669 --> 00:04:15,421
I really want to go there, too.
I wanna go so badly.

65
00:04:15,505 --> 00:04:17,715
It really was beautiful there.

66
00:04:19,175 --> 00:04:21,427
I haven't seen
anything like that in my life.

67
00:04:22,553 --> 00:04:25,265
So tell me, how was it? How did you feel?

68
00:04:25,348 --> 00:04:27,183
Yeah, it was good.

69
00:04:27,267 --> 00:04:29,477
Well, fine. Yeah. No change for me.

70
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,312
- No change? Okay.
- No.

71
00:04:31,396 --> 00:04:32,230
- Okay.
- Got it.

72
00:04:32,313 --> 00:04:35,108
- Yeah. No change for me.
- Mm-hmm.

73
00:04:35,191 --> 00:04:37,819
I think I was honestly
just a bit surprised

74
00:04:37,902 --> 00:04:40,822
that Hyeon-woo came on to me so strongly.

75
00:04:40,905 --> 00:04:43,116
YESTERDAY

76
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,909
Your your hands are so big.

77
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:56,587
You look better with your ears showing.

78
00:04:57,338 --> 00:04:59,632
- Huh? What?
- Oh, I'm sorry.

79
00:04:59,716 --> 00:05:01,092
You look better, though.

80
00:05:01,175 --> 00:05:03,011
- My ears are too small to tuck my--
- Cute.

81
00:05:03,094 --> 00:05:04,304
Oh, sorry.

82
00:05:05,096 --> 00:05:06,639
The way he expressed

83
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:10,643
his interest was a bit much at times.

84
00:05:10,727 --> 00:05:13,604
I was still in the process
of getting to know Hyeon-woo,

85
00:05:13,688 --> 00:05:15,940
but he was acting like
he was on a date with someone

86
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:18,651
who had already expressed
they had feelings for him.

87
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:23,573
Okay. Well, in that case,
I'm gonna take action as I see fit.

88
00:05:23,656 --> 00:05:24,866
And what action is that?

89
00:05:24,949 --> 00:05:28,119
I'm gonna have to keep you to myself.

90
00:05:28,202 --> 00:05:30,955
I'm taking a new approach now.
I thought about this yesterday.

91
00:05:31,039 --> 00:05:33,624
I thought about this a lot
while you were gone.

92
00:05:33,708 --> 00:05:34,917
Okay.

93
00:05:35,001 --> 00:05:37,795
Because yesterday, talking to the others

94
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,589
made me realize
you're getting too popular.

95
00:05:39,672 --> 00:05:42,884
- What do you mean I'm popular?
- You're so popular now.

96
00:05:42,967 --> 00:05:44,677
LAST NIGHT

97
00:05:44,761 --> 00:05:46,721
So have you made up your mind now, I-geon?

98
00:05:47,722 --> 00:05:49,349
Oh, yeah, I think I have now.

99
00:05:52,727 --> 00:05:53,644
Do we overlap?

100
00:05:56,147 --> 00:05:57,273
Yeah, I think we do.

101
00:05:59,025 --> 00:05:59,942
Right.

102
00:06:03,529 --> 00:06:06,407
If you had told me that you had
a change of heart from going there…

103
00:06:06,491 --> 00:06:07,325
Yeah.

104
00:06:08,242 --> 00:06:10,453
…then I guess things
would be different right now.

105
00:06:10,536 --> 00:06:13,414
But I'm happy to hear that
you haven't had a change of heart.

106
00:06:13,498 --> 00:06:14,749
Yeah, I'm glad.

107
00:06:15,958 --> 00:06:16,876
Really glad.

108
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:22,799
Sung-min is so convinced right now
that he is the one

109
00:06:22,882 --> 00:06:24,592
Go-eun has feelings for out of the guys.

110
00:06:24,675 --> 00:06:27,011
Well, the last time
they had a conversation,

111
00:06:27,095 --> 00:06:30,264
she did say she was certain
about her feelings towards him.

112
00:06:30,348 --> 00:06:34,435
But but she also said that
she wanted to keep him on his toes.

113
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:36,521
- Those were her exact words.
- Right.

114
00:06:36,604 --> 00:06:39,357
So how else is he supposed
to think about this?

115
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,525
Totally. For sure.

116
00:06:40,608 --> 00:06:42,276
So why doesn't it ring true to me?

117
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,529
I think she likes I-geon, not Sung-min.

118
00:06:44,612 --> 00:06:47,365
She made it sound like
she was talking about Sung-min,

119
00:06:47,448 --> 00:06:49,742
but we have no idea
who she actually meant.

120
00:06:51,744 --> 00:06:54,789
Things are about to get really
interesting from here on out.

121
00:06:54,872 --> 00:06:58,584
- Interesting? That's what you'd say?
- Yeah, interesting. That's all I can say.

122
00:06:58,668 --> 00:07:01,087
Mm. So I've been really
looking forward to today.

123
00:07:08,052 --> 00:07:10,346
When Go-eun and Hyeon-woo got back today,

124
00:07:12,974 --> 00:07:17,311
<i>I found myself avoiding looking at them.</i>

125
00:07:17,395 --> 00:07:19,856
I thought about why I did that.

126
00:07:19,939 --> 00:07:23,985
Uh… And I think it's because I was worried

127
00:07:24,068 --> 00:07:26,320
they'd be looking too happy
after their trip.

128
00:07:28,072 --> 00:07:32,618
I am planning to have a conversation
with Go-eun as soon as I get the chance.

129
00:07:32,702 --> 00:07:34,996
I just really want to tell her
my honest feelings.

130
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:37,999
I want her to know how I feel
and what's going through my mind.

131
00:07:38,082 --> 00:07:40,293
But I'll have to wait
till she has the time to talk.

132
00:07:40,376 --> 00:07:43,504
- We cooked and chopped firewood.
- You chopped firewood?

133
00:07:43,588 --> 00:07:44,839
Yeah.

134
00:07:46,382 --> 00:07:48,468
- Mina, you're back.
- I've come back.

135
00:07:48,551 --> 00:07:50,970
- Hey, let's go have a chat together.
- Yeah, sure.

136
00:07:51,053 --> 00:07:52,013
Is now a good time?

137
00:07:52,096 --> 00:07:53,764
- Yeah.
- Let's go. Yeah.

138
00:08:04,233 --> 00:08:07,612
She's having a chat with Mina Sue,
not Seung-il.

139
00:08:07,695 --> 00:08:09,655
I'm so curious to see how this will go.

140
00:08:10,823 --> 00:08:12,742
Let's go talk on the seesaw.

141
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:17,955
- So, how was it, Paradise?
- Honestly, well…

142
00:08:18,039 --> 00:08:20,583
I…

143
00:08:20,666 --> 00:08:25,963
I mean, it was fun,
but I'm not so sure anymore, honestly.

144
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:32,470
I actually wanted you to go
with Seung-il this time

145
00:08:32,553 --> 00:08:36,682
because whenever I try to ask him,
he wouldn't give me a clear answer.

146
00:08:36,766 --> 00:08:39,560
- So you thought--
- I wanted him to go there, talk to you,

147
00:08:39,644 --> 00:08:41,103
get to know you and clarify things.

148
00:08:41,187 --> 00:08:44,315
So if you had said to me before,
"I'm really curious about him.

149
00:08:44,398 --> 00:08:47,568
Having talked with him,
I really want to go to Paradise with him,"

150
00:08:47,652 --> 00:08:50,279
I would have told you to go
and have fun together.

151
00:08:50,363 --> 00:08:53,783
I would have told you to go enjoy yourself
without worrying about me.

152
00:08:53,866 --> 00:08:56,118
You were like,
"Don't worry, I want Su-been."

153
00:08:56,202 --> 00:08:58,204
Out of nowhere,
you're talking about Hyeon-woo.

154
00:08:58,287 --> 00:09:01,249
All of a sudden,
you're showing interest in Sung-min, too.

155
00:09:01,332 --> 00:09:04,377
So I was like, "Hang on.
What the hell? What's her deal?

156
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:07,088
Is she going from guy to guy?
Will she approach Seung-il next?"

157
00:09:07,171 --> 00:09:10,049
I can totally see
how you would've felt that way.

158
00:09:10,132 --> 00:09:11,884
I thought, "I need to talk to her."

159
00:09:11,968 --> 00:09:14,512
- I can't keep holding this anger inside.
- Okay.

160
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:16,472
I needed to have
this conversation with you.

161
00:09:16,556 --> 00:09:19,267
I just really want to know
what your feelings are

162
00:09:19,350 --> 00:09:22,270
and who you have feelings for now,
like, who you're set on.

163
00:09:25,398 --> 00:09:27,608
- They need to have it out.
- They do.

164
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:31,070
I've been interested in him all along.

165
00:09:31,153 --> 00:09:34,782
But the reason I never told you
was because…

166
00:09:34,865 --> 00:09:37,994
It's not that I've been jumping around
from one guy to another.

167
00:09:38,077 --> 00:09:40,454
- I don't think I have.
- You were curious about all of them.

168
00:09:40,538 --> 00:09:43,958
Kind of. No, it wasn't even that
I was curious about all of them.

169
00:09:44,041 --> 00:09:46,502
I've only been curious about a select few.

170
00:09:46,586 --> 00:09:50,840
But actually, on my first day here,
I gave my postcard to Seung-il.

171
00:09:50,923 --> 00:09:52,758
- Right from day one.
- Mm.

172
00:09:52,842 --> 00:09:53,759
And…

173
00:09:54,885 --> 00:09:58,014
Well, you know,
since you both looked so close,

174
00:09:58,097 --> 00:10:01,642
it wasn't easy for me to tell you
about little things like that

175
00:10:01,726 --> 00:10:03,436
that went on between me and him

176
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:06,439
because I know us girls
all talk together in our room,

177
00:10:06,522 --> 00:10:10,359
so it wasn't easy for me
to muscle in between you.

178
00:10:10,443 --> 00:10:12,612
That's why I never
said anything to you about it.

179
00:10:12,695 --> 00:10:14,697
I'm sure you were walking on egg shells.

180
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:17,241
I really didn't wanna step on your toes.

181
00:10:17,325 --> 00:10:19,619
So I just thought,
"Oh, well, it's unfortunate,

182
00:10:19,702 --> 00:10:21,537
but I won't get to know him right now."

183
00:10:21,621 --> 00:10:23,956
- But that made me feel rather--
- You're curious about him.

184
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:25,625
Yeah, I was curious, but also--

185
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:28,836
- My man is hot.
- Yeah, he's not bad.

186
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:31,422
But that made me feel
disappointed in myself

187
00:10:31,505 --> 00:10:35,468
because the whole point of coming on
this show is to make romantic connections.

188
00:10:35,551 --> 00:10:39,180
The fact that I was holding myself
back from doing that felt cowardly.

189
00:10:39,263 --> 00:10:41,641
It definitely took me
a few days to get there.

190
00:10:41,724 --> 00:10:44,352
Where do your feelings stand now,
after everything?

191
00:10:44,435 --> 00:10:47,772
I know that the decision is up to
Seung-il, at the end of the day,

192
00:10:47,855 --> 00:10:49,774
but I'm curious about your feelings.

193
00:10:49,857 --> 00:10:52,985
Who do you have feelings for?
Who are you still interested in?

194
00:10:53,569 --> 00:10:55,863
Yeah, we're curious about that, too.

195
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:01,535
But I'm curious about your feelings.
Who do you have feelings for?

196
00:11:01,619 --> 00:11:04,038
- Who are you still interested in?
- Right.

197
00:11:04,121 --> 00:11:08,501
Look, to be honest, I'm still interested
in all three of them right now.

198
00:11:08,584 --> 00:11:10,044
I'm still interested in Su-been,

199
00:11:10,127 --> 00:11:12,797
and I know I probably come across
as someone who wavers.

200
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,590
- It's okay.
- That's just who I am.

201
00:11:14,674 --> 00:11:17,593
You're right. This is just
who you are and how you operate.

202
00:11:17,677 --> 00:11:20,137
And this is how I am.
I can't help it either.

203
00:11:20,221 --> 00:11:22,890
It honestly feels like
Su-been was my first love

204
00:11:22,973 --> 00:11:25,976
because he was the first person
I went to Paradise with.

205
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:27,978
And then Seung-il is more like…

206
00:11:28,062 --> 00:11:31,107
Well, he's like…

207
00:11:32,108 --> 00:11:34,068
I'd like to be fully honest with you.

208
00:11:34,151 --> 00:11:37,238
Seung-il was very…
He was very straightforward with me.

209
00:11:37,321 --> 00:11:40,825
He actually told me that there were
only two people he was attracted to

210
00:11:40,908 --> 00:11:42,868
and wanted to get to know, you and me.

211
00:11:42,952 --> 00:11:46,414
So I think my feelings will change
depending on Seung-il's decision.

212
00:11:46,497 --> 00:11:49,166
- That's how I'm feeling right now.
- You're being fickle again.

213
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:51,001
- Yeah, you're right.
- You're wavering.

214
00:11:51,085 --> 00:11:52,503
I really am, aren't I?

215
00:11:52,586 --> 00:11:55,214
What I'm hearing is
you'll like anyone who likes you.

216
00:11:55,297 --> 00:11:57,550
That's true. I like guys who like me.

217
00:12:09,854 --> 00:12:13,149
- And you know what? Sometimes…
- Are you okay?

218
00:12:13,232 --> 00:12:16,235
Are you? You okay? Don't cry too much.

219
00:12:16,318 --> 00:12:17,361
- You good?
- I'm okay.

220
00:12:17,445 --> 00:12:19,530
Even if you had no interest before,

221
00:12:19,613 --> 00:12:23,117
once you find out someone likes you,
you start paying attention to them, right?

222
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,453
I think anyone can feel that way honestly.

223
00:12:25,536 --> 00:12:28,622
But what we can't understand is
due to a series of events,

224
00:12:28,706 --> 00:12:31,333
it looks like Mina Sue moves on
from person to person.

225
00:12:31,417 --> 00:12:33,419
But then it turns out
she still can't let go.

226
00:12:33,502 --> 00:12:35,713
What I find surprising is
even after the trip,

227
00:12:35,796 --> 00:12:37,840
- Seung-il is still on her list.
- I know.

228
00:12:37,923 --> 00:12:40,718
Or is it because
in this particular conversation,

229
00:12:40,801 --> 00:12:42,386
she doesn't want to kind of…

230
00:12:42,470 --> 00:12:44,847
- Let Min-gee win?
- Back down against Min-gee.

231
00:12:44,930 --> 00:12:46,932
That's why she's responding in this way.

232
00:12:47,016 --> 00:12:50,269
We've come too far now
to interpret it that way.

233
00:12:50,352 --> 00:12:52,313
I'm trying to understand
where she's coming from.

234
00:12:52,396 --> 00:12:56,650
I can't understand for the life of me
why she still thinks of Seung-il this way.

235
00:12:56,734 --> 00:12:59,445
She's only really carried a torch
for one person from the start,

236
00:12:59,528 --> 00:13:01,155
Su-been, Seung-il…

237
00:13:01,238 --> 00:13:03,282
You call that carrying a torch?

238
00:13:03,365 --> 00:13:05,451
The definition of carrying a torch is--

239
00:13:05,534 --> 00:13:08,120
She only has eyes for one,
one group of three guys.

240
00:13:08,204 --> 00:13:10,664
