563
00:32:38,957 --> 00:32:40,625
Ah, this is so tricky.

564
00:32:40,708 --> 00:32:41,876
Oh!

565
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:43,628
Ah, this is so tricky.

566
00:32:44,879 --> 00:32:46,297
Oh!

567
00:32:46,381 --> 00:32:47,799
Oh!

568
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:52,053
