but he's a bit sick of her.

577
00:33:25,253 --> 00:33:26,629
Pick on her, too.

578
00:33:32,552 --> 00:33:33,761
Oh.

579
00:33:34,387 --> 00:33:35,555
Oh.

580
00:33:36,723 --> 00:33:37,932
Oh.

581
00:33:38,016 --> 00:33:40,184
- Wow!
- No way!

582
00:33:40,268 --> 00:33:42,395
- Oh, oh.
