You kept asking me to close it.

648
00:37:12,605 --> 00:37:14,440
Close the hood. The window, I mean.

649
00:37:14,523 --> 00:37:16,651
- Put on your seat belt.
- Awesome.

650
00:37:16,734 --> 00:37:20,488
- Yesterday at lunch…
- But I'm pretty, too.

651
00:37:31,374 --> 00:37:33,251
Would you mind if we have a chat?

652
00:37:33,334 --> 00:37:35,294
- Yeah, sure.
- Great. Thanks.

653
00:37:36,087 --> 00:37:38,256
- Oh!
- Fighting fire with fire.

654
00:37:38,339 --> 00:37:40,216
This is the first time Min-gee's…

655
00:37:42,385 --> 00:37:44,679
