- Okay.

656
00:37:53,187 --> 00:37:56,482
<i>I resented him.</i>
<i>Actually, I resented him a lot.</i>

657
00:37:56,565 --> 00:37:57,900
I thought he'd come sit near me.

658
00:37:57,984 --> 00:38:02,071
I thought, "Is he sitting over there
because he's not interested in me?"

659
00:38:02,154 --> 00:38:04,490
But he didn't even
look at me once at lunch.

660
00:38:04,573 --> 00:38:06,450
He just kept talking to Mina Sue.

661
00:38:06,534 --> 00:38:10,121
Yeah, I know it's rude to leave
a table when others are still eating,

662
00:38:10,204 --> 00:38:14,292
