watching that. I couldn't sit through it.

663
00:38:14,375 --> 00:38:17,003
Of course she's upset,
after putting so much effort into winning.

664
00:38:17,086 --> 00:38:18,963
- You're right.
- She wanted him to come over

665
00:38:19,046 --> 00:38:20,798
