666
00:38:20,881 --> 00:38:22,800
And she's been waiting a long time.

667
00:38:26,637 --> 00:38:28,472
Hey, I'm actually done eating now.

668
00:38:28,556 --> 00:38:31,642
Hey, I'm actually done eating now,
so I'm gonna go and rest.

669
00:38:31,726 --> 00:38:33,644
- For sure.
- Enjoy your meals.

670
00:38:33,728 --> 00:38:36,188
Sorry to leave you guys. I'm so sorry.

671
