has totally shifted to her now.

686
00:39:30,534 --> 00:39:33,371
I'm not sure. I did talk to him a little.

687
00:39:33,454 --> 00:39:36,165
- Mina was sitting across from him, right?
- Yeah.

688
00:39:36,248 --> 00:39:39,960
