makes me wonder, you know.

689
00:39:40,044 --> 00:39:41,962
As soon as you left,
he was the first to ask,

690
00:39:42,046 --> 00:39:44,673
- "Is she not feeling well?"
- Mm.

691
00:39:48,427 --> 00:39:50,054
