692
00:39:50,137 --> 00:39:51,806
- Shall we talk?
- Let's do it.

693
00:39:51,889 --> 00:39:53,265
- Where?
- Around the back.

694
00:39:53,349 --> 00:39:55,142
- Where?
- Around the back.

695
00:39:55,226 --> 00:39:56,769
- Busy?
- I'll chat with him.

696
00:39:56,852 --> 00:39:58,646
- I'm gonna chat with him first.
- Why?

697
00:40:10,574 --> 00:40:13,035
Hmm, things feel a bit different today.

698
00:40:14,203 --> 00:40:15,579
Are you feeling sick?

699
00:40:15,663 --> 00:40:18,290
- No, I'm not sick.
- Okay.

700
00:40:18,374 --> 00:40:20,751
- It's just…
- You just didn't have an appetite?

701
00:40:20,835 --> 00:40:22,086
No, I didn't at all.

702
00:40:22,169 --> 00:40:25,756
Okay, so shall we start with how it went
in Paradise yesterday for you?

703
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:27,216
- Paradise?
- Yeah.

704
00:40:27,299 --> 00:40:29,760
