705
00:40:29,844 --> 00:40:31,345
- Oh.
- Yeah.

706
00:40:32,054 --> 00:40:33,764
Looks like their timing didn't line up.

707
00:40:33,848 --> 00:40:36,809
If only Su-been had come a little later.

708
00:40:36,892 --> 00:40:41,230
It's not like Su-been's interested in her.
It's just caused a big misunderstanding.

709
00:40:41,313 --> 00:40:43,983
If she has to make a decision,
she'll do the wrong thing.

710
00:40:44,066 --> 00:40:46,402
I just really hope
she gets to talk to Seung-il

711
00:40:46,485 --> 00:40:48,487
